						<p>Published in SII Vol XII, No: 107</p>						

						<p>This inscription records the gift of 11 <hi rend="italic">kaḻañju</hi> of gold for supplying water to the temple of Tiruppōndaip-perumāṉaḍigaḷ at Rājamallach-chaturvēdimaṅgalam, by a member of <hi rend="italic">āḷuṅgaṇam</hi> of Kāvitippākkam in Paḍuvūrk-kōṭṭam.</p>						

